text:
@HumanProgress Correct, Earth is not about to run out of anything.

Long-term, the easy to reach oil &amp; gas will deplete and hydrocarbon energy will become very expensive, but not run out.

Large increases in CO2 ppm do cause increased temperatures and above 1000 ppm will feel stuffy.

