e in appearance and behavior, as noted in the Dartmouth source; Meloni's poised black suit ensemble reflects this ideal.

- Meloni, Italy's first female Prime Minister since 2022 and leader of the right-wing Brothers of Italy party, often uses fashion strategically, as seen in her preference for Armani suits during key political moments, a tactic to project power and redefine Italy's global image, according to the 2022 New York Times article.

- The post captures a moment from April 26, 2025, likely during a formal event, where Meloni's style—elegant yet understated—aligns with her political persona, balancing her hard-right roots with a moderated image to counter neo-fascist critiques, as mentioned in the Wikipedia entry."}]}, "is_translatable": false, "legacy": {"bookmark_count": 30, "bookmarked": false, "conversation_id_str": "1916127890749722651", "created_at": "Sun Apr 27 17:17:08 +0000 2025", "display_text_range": [17, 40], "entities": {"hashtags": [], "symbols": [], "timestamps": [], "urls": [{"display_url": "x.com/i/grok/share/A…", "expanded_url": "https://x.com/i/grok/share/AxW6RIvFWnLfADJ8h2TID1yBb", "indices": [17, 40], "url": "https://t.co/88Xeats4FX"}], "user_mentions": [{"id_str": "47737880", "indices": [0, 16], "name": "Mambo Italiano", "screen_name": "mamboitaliano__"}]}, "favorite_count": 648, "favorited": false, "full_text": "@mamboitaliano__ https://t.co/88Xeats4FX", "id_str": "1916542141787930812", "in_reply_to_screen_name": "mamboitaliano__", "in_reply_to_status_id_str": "1916127890749722651", "in_reply_to_user_id_str": "47737880", "is_quote_status": false, "lang": "qme", "possibly_sensitive": false, "possibly_sensitive_editable": true, "quote_count": 9, "reply_count": 108, "retweet_count": 62, "retweeted": false, "user_id_str": "44196397"}, "rest_id": "1916542141787930812", "source": "<a href="http://twitter.com/download/iphone" rel="nofollow">Twitter for iPhone</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "29638", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}

